latestPosts.caption:
A little glimpse from my sister’s big day ♥️🧿

Always dreamt of making it magical for her !💫
From curating every outfit to those endless last-minute runs,
It felt like prepping for the most emotional exam ever…
chaotic, beautiful, and full of love🥹♥️
She found her forever, and that’s what truly mattered.
We don’t have many pictures together,
but the memories live forever and here I am leaving a piece of it ,forever on my feed ♥️
